				<td colspan="2"><span>I went in fear like 3 day ago to kill CT and is attached golems.. I used fade to split them and it worked. Afaik they see invis.
<br />

<br />
As for the enraged Imp, he was already spawned when we zoned in and jumped on us. Aggro range is pretty huge so no clue where he was from.
<br />

<br />
Fading in fear see invis mob is pretty risky indeed due to aggro being so wide. Although i didnt used fade vs the trash we were pulling them ~20 at a time
<br />

<br />
And so far i can ganranteed fade work vs see invis mob, if your are out of aggro range on the next tick after you faded.</span></td>
